Instructions to run Teammates test system

1. Checkout the `test` folder and import into Eclipse (Eclipse, right click Package Explorer -> Import -> Existing Projects into Workspace, navigate to the newly extracted folder)
2. Open Config.java:
- Change BROWSER constant to the appropriate browser [1]
- Make sure the accounts you typed in (in Config.java) as Coordinator has real coordinator access of Teammates system
3. Make sure you have Firefox (v3/v4) or Chrome (or whichever browsers to be tested on) installed. 
4. Starting the Selenium Server: Run selenium_server.bat
5. Run the individual tests from eclipse project (class file starts with Test, e.g. TestCoordinatorLogin)

[1] Browser tables:
Firefox *firefox
Chrome	*googlechrome

Created: June 08, 2011